V 284
allow a NULL parameter to be passed to RT_HIT_NORMAL if they don't have a normal array to be filled in and just want hitp->hit_normal to be calculated.  this makes it pretty trivial to update code that used RT_HIT_NORM() over to RT_HIT_NORMAL() by just adding a NULL and 0 flip value.
